---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import TopBanner from '../../components/TopBanner.astro';
import Navbar from '../../components/Navbar.astro';
import PageHeader from '../../components/PageHeader.astro';
import CTABanner from '../../components/CTABanner.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import heroImage from '../../assets/images/representation/greenland/greenland-banner.webp';
import WorkingCommittee from '../../components/WorkingCommittee.astro';
---

<Layout title="Greenland - FiNAN">
  <main>
    <TopBanner />
    <Navbar />
    <PageHeader
      title="Greenland"
      description="Experience unique healthcare challenges in Greenland, the world's largest island, serving diverse communities across vast Arctic landscapes."
      backgroundImage={heroImage}
      backgroundAlt="Nuuk, Greenland"
    />

    <section class="bg-white py-16">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6">
        <header class="max-w-2xl">
          <h2
            class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 md:text-4xl"
          >
            Healthcare in Greenland
          </h2>
        </header>

        <div class="mt-4">
          <p class="mb-6 text-lg text-gray-700">
            Greenland presents extraordinary opportunities for Filipino
            healthcare professionals seeking to make a meaningful impact in one
            of the world's most unique healthcare environments. As an autonomous
            territory within Denmark, Greenland offers the chance to serve
            diverse communities across vast Arctic landscapes while being part
            of the Danish healthcare system.
          </p>

          <p class="mb-6 text-lg text-gray-700">
            With a population of approximately 56,000 people spread across the
            world's largest island, healthcare delivery in Greenland requires
            innovation, adaptability, and cultural sensitivity. Healthcare
            professionals here play vital roles in community health, often
            serving as the primary medical contact for remote settlements.
          </p>

          <h3
            class="mb-4 text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 md:text-3xl"
          >
            Unique Healthcare Challenges
          </h3>
          <p class="mb-6 text-lg text-gray-700">
            Greenland's healthcare system operates under Danish standards but is
            adapted to Arctic conditions and geographic isolation. The main
            hospital in Nuuk serves as the central facility, with smaller health
            centers and nursing stations distributed across coastal communities.
            Healthcare professionals often work with telemedicine technology and
            may travel by helicopter or boat to reach patients.
          </p>

          <h3
            class="mb-4 text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 md:text-3xl"
          >
            Arctic Life and Culture
          </h3>
          <p class="mb-6 text-lg text-gray-700">
            Living in Greenland means experiencing the midnight sun, northern
            lights, and some of the world's most spectacular natural phenomena.
            The Greenlandic culture blends Inuit traditions with modern Nordic
            influences, creating a welcoming community that values healthcare
            professionals who serve remote populations with dedication and
            cultural respect.
          </p>

          <h3
            class="mb-4 text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 md:text-3xl"
          >
            Professional Impact
          </h3>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">
            Healthcare professionals in Greenland have the opportunity to make a
            profound difference in community health outcomes while experiencing
            one of the world's last frontiers. The work is challenging but
            rewarding, offering unique clinical experiences, cultural exchange,
            and the satisfaction of serving communities where healthcare access
            can be life-changing.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <WorkingCommittee country="greenland" />
    <CTABanner />
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
